Karneval is a Japanese manga series by Touya Mikanagi, originally starting serialization in the monthly josei manga magazine Monthly Comic Zero Sum published by Ichijinsha in early 2008. There are currently eleven volumes released in Japan. An anime adaptation was announced in April 2012 and premiered on April 3, 2013.
